 $Id$ 

 VGM Example E01
 Converting geometry from Geant4 to Root
 --------------------------------------
 
 Source: Geant4 novice N03 example
         
 1. Define environment variables 
    (see doc/INSTALL)
    
 2. Install Geant4 N03 example in E02 directory:
    cp -r ${G4INSTALL}/examples/novice/N03 .
    source env_setup.csh
    
 3. Copy provided files into the example:
    cp GNUmakefile N03
    cp ExN03DetectorConstruction.cc N03/src
    
 4. Recompile 
    cd N03
    gmake
    
 5. Run example, the geometry will be exported during initialization
    exampleN03
 
 6. Open and view the generated Root file 
    root
    root [0] gSystem->Load("libGeom");
    root [1] new TGeoManager("N03", "Geant4 novice example N03");
    root [2] gGeoManager->Import("N03Example.root");
    root [3] TBrowser b;
    root [4] gGeoManager->GetTopVolume()->Draw();

                
